assignments.name: messageData
assignments.value:
={{ {
  phoneNumber: $('Webhook Classifier').item.json.body.data.key.remoteJid.split('@')[0],
  messageType: $('Webhook Classifier').item.json.body.data.messageType,
  messageText: $('Webhook Classifier').item.json.body.data.message?.conversation || $('Webhook Classifier').item.json.body.data.message?.extendedTextMessage?.text || '',
  imageCaption: $('Webhook Classifier').item.json.body.data.message?.imageMessage?.caption || '',
  hasAudio: $('Webhook Classifier').item.json.body.data.messageType === 'audioMessage',
  hasImage: $('Webhook Classifier').item.json.body.data.messageType === 'imageMessage',
  timestamp: $('Webhook Classifier').item.json.body.data.messageTimestamp,
  pushName: $('Webhook Classifier').item.json.body.data.pushName,
  userId: $json.id,
  base64: $('Webhook Classifier').item.json.body.data?.message?.base64
} }}
